Hello Girlz 
In order to run this project succefuly you must follow some instructions :

1- You should create a local database in phpMySql name it : PFM (it's mandatory)
2- To continue the development you must create a test table name it Test and add only two Columns (id & name) id is the primary key and you must activate the auto increment option & name is varchar(255); 

3- It's optional, you can add you data to your table to test for example afficher method 



Thank you for you're commitment and hard work have a greate development
====================================================================================================================================
When Creating a table in ManageDataBase.php we have to grant PHP the permission to write in our hard drive so we can create a subClass that inherit from ManageTable class and so our new class will have all the tables functionalities